    How does BookBag work?
  </div>
  <div class="column">
    <img class="icon" src="assets/add.png">
    <h3>Add Books</h3>
    Scan the barcode with your phone, or enter the ISBN of the book, and we take care of the rest.
  </div>
  <div class="column">
    <img class="icon" src="assets/book.png">
    <h3>View Books</h3>
    Search by title or author for the book you want and we will see if anyone has listed it as available.
  </div>
  <div class="column">
    <img class="icon" src="assets/check.png">
    <h3>Checkout Books</h3>
