<div class="section">
  <div class="title">
    Frequently Asked Questions
  </div>
  <div class="text-block align-left">
    <div class="question">Who can check out my books?</div>
    <div class="answer">Only verified users who have logged into their account will be able to check out books.</div>

    <div class="question">Do I have to add my books to check out books?</div>
    <div class="answer">No, you do not have to list your own library to checkout books. However, in the spirit of community we heavily encourage you to add the books you are willing to let others borrow.</div>

    <div class="question">Is this only for professors?</div>
    <div class="answer">Not at all! The goal is for any member of the LeTourneau community to create an account and gain access to literary wealth of people's personal collections.</div>
  </div>
</div>


